timelineItems.desc:
Simon Borg talks to FC Dallas Head Coach Oscar Pareja about the club's playoff chances as they prepare for their Wildcard match against the Vancouver Whitecaps on Wednesday night. Pareja, in his first season back on the FC Dallas coaching staff, has guided the club to 4th place in the Western Conference after finishing 8th in 2013. 

Catch FC Dallas vs. Vancouver Whitecaps on Wednesday at 9pm ET on TSN 1 and MLS Live.

timelineItems.desc: Jason Saghini, Andrew Wiebe and special guest "The Coach" Jesse Marsch dive deep into Wednesday's knockout round matchup between the Vancouver Whitecaps and FC Dallas.
